{"tid":2156333,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"PK何以心情舒暢 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-08-14T11:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T11:14:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b97bf2909c9101cb54a295ee5a5e2e25a1c237c8","tid":2156333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200721/MWVJDUXX35CR3CIHN7NYABT6KU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200721%2FMWVJDUXX35CR3CIHN7NYABT6KU%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=2b5f8df0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200721%2FMWVJDUXX35CR3CIHN7NYABT6KU%2F&h=61db3555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200721/MWVJDUXX35CR3CIHN7NYABT6KU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nPK何以心情舒暢 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7S9gGP8qD9Wquk_hRmgQYbQltj8=/5832x3944/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MSCO7PJJXNCONG5V36VRQGXUZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7S9gGP8qD9Wquk_hRmgQYbQltj8%3D%2F5832x3944%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMSCO7PJJXNCONG5V36VRQGXUZE.jpg&h=37bb1967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被美國制裁的PK鄧接受01訪問，訪問出街時間夾到正，正好挑機蘋果日報，對#FreeJimmy與Agnes的人嗤之以鼻。PK訪問中自稱得悉被制裁後，心情舒暢。香港人七成抑鬱，得佢一支公心情舒暢，老天都會妒忌。太老定舒暢，招惹北大人猜疑，條友係咪美帝「鬼」？。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n一，家有急事，幫全家三代改名換姓，避過制裁。有仔生嘅話，改名做鄧小平。<br />\n<br />\n二，。。。。。。。。。腎虛驚肚屙的話，叫工會送佢菠蘿。<br />\n<br />\n三，與京官一同上榜，光榮到震，。。。。。。。。。。拷問吓你個偷麻將牌警長下屬，係咪想碰三萬，thx？<br />\n<br />\n四，銀行落閘，注定要搬錢返屋企收埋。僭建地牢，鄭司長與老公是「專家」，學吓嘢。<br />\n<br />\n五，澄清將蘋果日報丟去回收箱那個四眼佬唔係自己的孿生細佬後，。。。。。。。。。"}]}